    <content>&lt;P&gt;It is quite a broad request. I would suggest starting with the &lt;STRONG&gt;learning journeys&lt;/STRONG&gt; at &lt;A href="https://learning.sap.com/artificial-intelligence" target="_blank" rel="noopener noreferrer"&gt;https://learning.sap.com/artificial-intelligence&lt;/A&gt; and to narrow down to more specific questions posted here. Best regards.&lt;/P&gt;&lt;P&gt;&lt;span class="lia-inline-image-display-wrapper lia-image-align-inline" image-alt="VitaliyR_0-1732118332956.png" style="width: 400px;"&gt;&lt;img src="https://community.sap.com/t5/image/serverpage/image-id/193429i68E3B1D698C4418D/image-size/medium?v=v2&amp;amp;px=400" role="button" title="VitaliyR_0-1732118332956.png" alt="VitaliyR_0-1732118332956.png" /&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/P&gt;&lt;P&gt;&amp;nbsp;&lt;/P&gt;</content>
